{"tid":734861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網上熱話】林超英憂扶手甩漆傳播有毒物質　港鐵：不會損害健康 (11:00)","createTime":"2018-07-09T04:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:17:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31ed0b171b0fb1050de71e49c7eda8fd5acf8993","tid":734861,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"港鐵車廂內，不時聽到廣播提醒乘客緊握扶手以保安全。不過前天文台長林超英日前於facebook發帖批評港鐵車廂扶手油漆磨損，憂慮會把有毒物質「贈送」乘客。港鐵回覆《明報》稱，車廂用料包括扶手油漆在內，「不會對人體健康構成損害」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林超英上周六（7日）上載一張港鐵車廂圖片，圖中原本黃色的扶手因油漆磨損，變成部分銀色。他於帖文中指出，扶手油漆磨損除了礙眼，更可能把有毒物質「贈送」給乘客，又稱有關情況已存在超過一年，要求港鐵盡快修補扶手，「不要破壞香港形象」。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引起網民關注。林超英向《明報》表示，扶手油漆剝落屬於非常明顯「甩漏」，加上興建鐵路時的錯漏，令市民對港鐵營運失去信心：「香港人是港鐵的真正大老闆，港鐵必須以香港總體利益為重，叫價不得過分，條件不可過苛，否則社會將大反彈。」<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆《明報》指，車廂用料包括扶手油漆在內，「不會對人體健康構成損害」，而港鐵收到車廂保養相關查詢後，會記錄並清潔及跟進。<br />\n<br />\n林超英則說，「可能把有毒物質贈送給乘客」屬誇張表達手法，稱「有毒物質」借代油漆。他強調，帖文是想突顯港鐵「無鬼用」，無保好車廂保養，損害香港形象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180709/s00001/1531095837315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180709%2Fs00001%2F1531095837315&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=42a9df0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180709%2Fs00001%2F1531095837315&h=fbf38e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180709/s00001/1531095837315</a>"},{"pid":"50b7365de114c743c1347412d2e93679495e913d","tid":734861,"uid":11719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"你無聽過有害物質不會損害健康咩？"},{"pid":"6e0adbe64706e37e69ea6800749f8a4b566caaea","tid":734861,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"有毒無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3861cf172ad5fb88e59737c142b29c901f973181","tid":734861,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體jpg 個張"},{"pid":"dfca2771f318084ad646b5eda5fef1c774df4ed1","tid":734861,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"50b7365de114c743c1347412d2e93679495e913d","tid":734861,"uid":11719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"你無聽過有害物質不會損害健康咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔會架wo<br />\n你唔係以為會呀on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3149b50f546a6512456ee5fe073350b7cd9de93","tid":734861,"uid":120783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3861cf172ad5fb88e59737c142b29c901f973181","tid":734861,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體jpg 個張"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/161710_d052d19a4d6dc20b8194642a92b45d02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F161710_d052d19a4d6dc20b8194642a92b45d02.png&h=902802cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}